RUNTIME DEPENDENCIES (Flutter/Dart packages, used as-is, unmodified)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

flutter_soloud
  License : MIT License (see the package page on pub.dev)
  URL     : https://pub.dev/packages/flutter_soloud
  Use     : The one native dependency. flu_doom's audio engine produces PCM
            entirely in Dart (DMX SFX decode + the Nuked-OPL3 music render);
            flutter_soloud is the low-latency native backend that plays those
            in-memory PCM/WAV buffers (loadMem), mixing many concurrent voices
            with per-voice volume and stereo pan on macOS / iOS / Android.

